{"id":"e9abfcf6-77d6-43c2-a0c1-46827ba7db42","name":"Dragon Ball Z S.H. Figuarts Action Figure Android 19 13cm","slug":"dragon-ball-z-s.h.-figuarts-action-figur-1-2","description":"<p><b>Dragon Ball Z </b>Action Figure of <b>Android 19 </b>in <b>S.H. Figuarts </b>collection, size approx.13cm. <b>Official product</b> by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Android 19 </strong>from \"<strong>Dragon Ball Z</strong>\" joins <strong>S.H.Figuarts</strong>! Optional expressions let you capture his early appearances with a \"right glance\" expression part, plus shouting, smirking, and frightened faces. In combination with a optional head without hat, you can replicate all sorts of scenes! Other accessories include a variety of optional hands and a broken arm option. And it even includes a bonus option expression for the S.H.Figuarts <strong>SUPER SAIYAN VEGETA</strong> -AWAKENED SUPER SAIYAN BLOOD- figure (sold separately)!</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><strong>Contents :</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Main Body</li>\n<li>Three pairs of optional hands</li>\n<li>Four optional expressions</li>\n<li>Optional pair of arms</li>\n<li>Optional head</li>\n<li>Bonus option expression for the S.H.Figuarts SUPER SAIYAN VEGETA -AWAKENED SUPER SAIYAN BLOOD- figure(sold separately)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This product is not a toy or product for children. It is a collectors item intended for adults only.</p>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-25T23:55:38.449Z","updatedAt":"2025-03-25T23:55:38.449Z","barcode":"4573102650313","deletedAt":null,"brandId":"3973100e-a304-42f2-b48a-5e810adf1082","franchiseId":null,"seriesId":null,"lineId":null,"categories":[{"productId":"e9abfcf6-77d6-43c2-a0c1-46827ba7db42","categoryId":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570","category":{"id":"bc7dcae3-c133-443f-85e0-737ca2ab3570",